com.vector.cfg.model.groovy.api

Interface IMdfWriteListAddTypeExtensions<T extends MIObject>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IMdfWriteListExtensions<O,R,D>

    @PublishedApi(value=ADDITIONS_ALLOWED)
 @PublishedApiDomain(value=AUTOMATION_IF)
public interface IMdfWriteListAddTypeExtensions<T extends MIObject>
    The interface IMdfWriteListAddTypeExtensions defines some method extensions for MDF child lists to create and add new MDF object instances.

    (c) Copyright Vctr Informatik GmbH. All Rights Reserved.
